data.description: Welcome to Orchard Lane! This 2 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage townhome is waiting for you to move right in. Enjoy having an upper and lower living space and a bathroom on each level. If you are looking for an affordable property, this townhome offers a low association fee, no work needed and the seller is willing to offer $5,000 towards your interest rate buy down/ closing costs! Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants and I-94.Come make this townhouse your home!
